Claws with GreatStrike - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Claws-GreatStrike-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Great Strike - Claws&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a **Great Strike** Claws attack*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<4cs>8 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[1d8!cf<0cs>100 [Great Strike]]] [Great Strike] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods]]] + [[ [[@{Selected|Charisma_mod} [Cha]]] [Cha] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Slashing &#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[2]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[4]] Slashing + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Advantage-Nested
