Claws with GreatStrike - Unnested Macros - Works on it's own, but not in a nested query
---------------------------------------------
Claws-GreatStrike-Cha-Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Great Strike - Claws}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a **Great Strike** Claws attack*}} [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<4cs>8 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[1d8!cf<0cs>100 [Great Strike]]] [Great Strike] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Charisma_mod} [Cha] ]] [Cha] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Slashing }}{{Dice Mods=$[[2]] Varies}} {{Static=$[[4]] Slashing + $[[5]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** }} {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals slashing damage you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.}} 
---------------------------------------------
