Claws with Slasher - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Claws-Slasher-Cha-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-Disadvantage3-Nested}} 
---------------------------------------------
Claws-Slasher-Cha-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Attack - Claws&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Claws attack*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<1cs>8 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Charisma_mod} [Cha]]] [Cha] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Slashing&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Slashing + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[6]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals slashing damage you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125; {{Slasher Crit=When you score a critical hit that deals slashing damage to a creature you grievously wound it. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls.&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
