---------------------------------------------
Claws with Magic Weapon and Slasher - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Claws-Slasher-Cha-MW-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
